Package: libgtksourcecompletion-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libgtksourcecompletion1 (= ${Source-Version}) libgtksourceview2.0-dev (>=2.0.0)
Description: Development files of libgtksourcecompletion
 This library contains a generic popup to add completion 
 support to GtkSourceView. It has some default events and
 a document words provider that adds (auto)completion of
 previously written words

